             depos'd, That the Prisoner and himself did the Fact. They took out the Pin and the Bar, and Berry took down the Shutter, and he went in, opened the Door, and let in Berry, and they carried away the Things mentioned in the Indictment, but not having Time could not carry away any more, for it was at that Time Break of Day. The Prisoner deny'd the Fact, and call'd Persons to his Reputation. The Jury found him <rs id="t17241014-18-verdict94" type="verdictDescription">
